---
title: Fiery Sesame Pork Bowls with coriander and bell pepper
description: If you think you can handle the heat, then this spicy sesame pork bowl recipe is definitely one to try. Featuring fragrant rice, plenty of veg and, of course, some fiery flavour, you're going to love this Asian-inspired dish.
